"Co-operative Business Consultants (CBC) is a co-operative consortium dedicated to helping democratic enterprises to start up, grow and thrive. For over a decade it has delivered high quality advice, mentoring, training and research on business development and financial planning, governance, legal structures, human resources and other key issues crucial to co-ops."
